60|$|We {{passed the}} bridge, {{and soon after}} that <b>I</b> <b>asked</b> if she saw the lock. She said no, {{she did not see}} any lock; <b>and</b> <b>I</b> said, “Oh!” <b>and</b> pulled on. Another five minutes went by, <b>and</b> then <b>I</b> <b>asked</b> <b>her</b> to look again.|$|R
